1
00:00:03,466 --> 00:00:06,426
=Please Don't Spoil Me=
=Episod 16=

2
00:00:06,810 --> 00:00:09,680
Awak akan dijatuhi 30 sebatan,
kemudian diusir ke istana dingin.

3
00:00:10,410 --> 00:00:12,880
Jangan, tuanku maharani!

4
00:00:21,570 --> 00:00:24,000
Beta beri awak peluang terakhir.

5
00:00:24,570 --> 00:00:25,620
Awak masih sempat berubah fikiran.

6
00:00:26,690 --> 00:00:27,900
Patik dah bertekad.

7
00:00:28,070 --> 00:00:29,460
Sila mulakan hukuman, tuanku maharani.

8
00:00:30,490 --> 00:00:31,400
Baik.

9
00:00:32,180 --> 00:00:32,820
Pukul dia.

10
00:00:36,100 --> 00:00:37,930
Sakitnya!

11
00:00:39,680 --> 00:00:40,280
Berhenti!

12
00:00:41,930 --> 00:00:42,650
(Qin Yu?)

13
00:00:43,030 --> 00:00:44,500
(Kenapa dia datang sini?)

14
00:00:48,350 --> 00:00:48,930
Anakanda.

15
00:00:49,950 --> 00:00:51,140
Kenapa anakanda datang ke sini?

16
00:00:55,640 --> 00:00:57,080
Gundik Rong, beta terlambat.

17
00:00:57,300 --> 00:00:58,470
Kenapa tuanku datang sini?

18
00:00:58,470 --> 00:00:59,940
Jangan campur tangan.

19
00:00:59,940 --> 00:01:01,030
Jangan risau, beta ada di sini.

20
00:01:01,360 --> 00:01:01,830
Awak dah selamat.

21
00:01:02,030 --> 00:01:03,550
(Apa yang selamatnya?)

22
00:01:03,550 --> 00:01:05,240
(Awak cuma rosakkan rancangan saya.)

23
00:01:06,330 --> 00:01:07,100
Bonda,

24
00:01:07,520 --> 00:01:08,670
apakah kesalahan Gundik Rong

25
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:10,060
sehingga bonda bertindak sedemikian?

26
00:01:11,230 --> 00:01:12,330
Gundik Rong

27
00:01:12,710 --> 00:01:14,620
tak menghormati orang
dan bersikap biadab.

28
00:01:15,230 --> 00:01:16,900
Bonda cuma ingin ajar dia.

29
00:01:17,430 --> 00:01:17,860
Kenapa?

30
00:01:18,650 --> 00:01:19,990
Adakah anakanda mahu halang bonda?

31
00:01:21,610 --> 00:01:22,820
Gundik Rong ialah gundik anakanda.

32
00:01:23,180 --> 00:01:24,010
Jika dia buat kesalahan,

33
00:01:24,010 --> 00:01:25,220
anakanda yang sepatutnya ajar dia.

34
00:01:25,970 --> 00:01:26,740
Rasanya bonda

35
00:01:27,270 --> 00:01:28,440
tak sepatutnya
campur tangan dalam perkara ini.

36
00:01:28,560 --> 00:01:29,170
Anakanda.

37
00:01:30,170 --> 00:01:31,860
Adakah anakanda mahu melawan bonda

38
00:01:32,530 --> 00:01:34,220
demi seorang gundik?

39
00:01:36,620 --> 00:01:38,480
Biasanya anakanda sangat hormati bonda.

40
00:01:39,670 --> 00:01:40,960
Anakanda pasti takkan campur tangan

41
00:01:41,510 --> 00:01:42,800
dalam perkara lain.

42
00:01:43,220 --> 00:01:43,860
Namun hari ini,

43
00:01:44,720 --> 00:01:45,980
anakanda bertekad mahu
melindungi Gundik Rong!

44
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:52,780
♪Saya cuma nampak awak sekilas,
awak beri saya tanggapan mendalam♪

45
00:01:52,780 --> 00:01:57,670
♪Saya berjanji untuk
bersama awak seumur hidup ini♪

46
00:01:57,670 --> 00:02:01,490
♪Bukit dan sungai telah
mengukuhkan cinta kita♪

47
00:02:01,490 --> 00:02:02,080
Awak tiada apa-apa?

48
00:02:02,380 --> 00:02:03,460
Tuanku cubalah

49
00:02:03,460 --> 00:02:04,410
disebat beberapa kali!

50
00:02:05,460 --> 00:02:06,100
Ini salah beta.

51
00:02:06,530 --> 00:02:07,410
Beta terlewat.

52
00:02:08,110 --> 00:02:10,160
Kenapa tuanku pergi ke sana?
Tuanku tak patut pergi.

53
00:02:10,690 --> 00:02:11,220
Beta tahu,

54
00:02:11,460 --> 00:02:12,470
awak sedang marah pada beta.

55
00:02:12,470 --> 00:02:13,370
Apa yang tuanku tahu?

56
00:02:13,370 --> 00:02:14,390
Tuanku tak tahu apa-apa.

57
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:16,640
(Sia-sia saja)

58
00:02:16,720 --> 00:02:17,780
(saya menanggung sepuluh sebatan.)

59
00:02:19,630 --> 00:02:20,510
Sebelum ini, awak selamatkan

60
00:02:20,820 --> 00:02:21,820
beta ketika di luar istana.

61
00:02:22,610 --> 00:02:23,650
Tentang lukisan
pengaturan pertahanan pula,

62
00:02:23,950 --> 00:02:25,940
awak berjaya halangnya daripada dicuri.

63
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:27,410
Awak selamatkan beta sekali lagi.

64
00:02:28,590 --> 00:02:29,510
Hari ini, awak berbalah
dengan maharani balu

65
00:02:29,820 --> 00:02:30,960
kerana beta,

66
00:02:31,820 --> 00:02:33,230
sebab itu dikenakan sebatan.

67
00:02:34,290 --> 00:02:35,120
Jika dikira,

68
00:02:36,150 --> 00:02:37,910
beta memang banyak
berhutang pada awak.

69
00:02:39,460 --> 00:02:40,040
Demi balas budi awak,

70
00:02:41,200 --> 00:02:42,920
beritahu saja beta permintaan awak,

71
00:02:43,440 --> 00:02:44,260
beta akan tunaikannya.

72
00:02:44,630 --> 00:02:46,350
Apa-apa saja?

73
00:02:46,710 --> 00:02:47,050
Tentulah.

74
00:02:48,210 --> 00:02:49,040
Tuanku takkan mungkir janji?

75
00:02:50,200 --> 00:02:51,060
Beta takkan mungkir janji.

76
00:02:51,650 --> 00:02:51,970
Baik.

77
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:54,310
Kalau begitu, tolong tunaikan
satu permintaan patik.

78
00:02:54,990 --> 00:02:55,370
Cakaplah.

79
00:02:55,640 --> 00:02:56,430
Patik mahu pulang ke istana dingin.

80
00:02:59,620 --> 00:03:01,490
Tuanku, masa untuk bersantap.

81
00:03:02,840 --> 00:03:03,380
Beritahu beta,

82
00:03:04,770 --> 00:03:05,560
adakah beta maharaja yang bebal?

83
00:03:06,510 --> 00:03:09,250
Tuanku rajin uruskan pentadbiran
dan ambil berat akan rakyat.

84
00:03:09,690 --> 00:03:11,850
Tuanku ialah maharaja
baik yang jarang ada.

85
00:03:12,330 --> 00:03:13,820
Mustahil tuanku bebal.

86
00:03:14,300 --> 00:03:15,860
Namun Gundik Rong
sanggup tinggal di istana dingin

87
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:18,160
demi menjauhkan diri daripada beta.

88
00:03:19,560 --> 00:03:20,980
Dia begitu benci pada beta?

89
00:03:21,470 --> 00:03:24,530
(Astaka Taman Tasik Batu Jed)
Gundik Rong tak benci pada tuanku.

90
00:03:25,170 --> 00:03:27,120
Gundik Rong pernah mempertaruhkan
nyawanya untuk selamatkan tuanku.

91
00:03:27,660 --> 00:03:29,140
Semasa tuanku mengalami keracunan,

92
00:03:29,380 --> 00:03:32,350
dia masak dan hantar ubat kepada tuanku.

93
00:03:33,070 --> 00:03:34,210
Kali ini, dia dikenakan sebatan

94
00:03:34,830 --> 00:03:37,440
sebab cuba menasihati maharani balu

95
00:03:37,440 --> 00:03:39,270
agar jangan berlawan dengan tuanku.

96
00:03:40,030 --> 00:03:41,180
Pada pendapat patik,

97
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:44,180
perasaan cinta Gundik Rong

98
00:03:44,850 --> 00:03:46,480
terhadap tuanku sangat mendalam

99
00:03:47,110 --> 00:03:48,500
dan mengharukan.

100
00:03:50,060 --> 00:03:51,580
Namun, kenapa dia bertekad

101
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:53,350
mahu pergi ke istana dingin?

102
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:55,030
Mungkin

103
00:03:55,910 --> 00:03:57,330
Gundik Rong ada rancangan lain.

104
00:03:58,490 --> 00:03:59,280
Dia sengaja berundur

105
00:03:59,980 --> 00:04:01,070
dan cuba mengurangkan kewaspadaan musuh.

106
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:02,750
Li Zhiduo,

107
00:04:03,220 --> 00:04:04,740
awak ialah sida-sida,

108
00:04:05,390 --> 00:04:07,050
tapi sangat memahami wanita.

109
00:04:08,700 --> 00:04:09,780
Beta rasa lega sikit

110
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:11,350
selepas sedar tentang semua ini.

111
00:04:12,020 --> 00:04:12,520
Masa untuk bersantap.

112
00:04:12,870 --> 00:04:13,450
Ya.

113
00:04:20,380 --> 00:04:22,420
Puan gembira sangat sebab

114
00:04:22,420 --> 00:04:23,660
dapat kembali ke istana dingin?

115
00:04:23,660 --> 00:04:24,740
Tentulah.

116
00:04:24,740 --> 00:04:26,340
Saya rasa istana dingin

117
00:04:26,340 --> 00:04:27,580
ialah tempat yang
paling selesa di dunia ini.

118
00:04:27,580 --> 00:04:28,900
(Istana Lanxin)

119
00:04:30,490 --> 00:04:32,380
Saya dah kembali!

120
00:04:32,500 --> 00:04:33,100
Jom!

121
00:04:41,958 --> 00:04:45,088
♪Dengar, bunyi pasang surut♪

122
00:04:45,248 --> 00:04:47,278
♪Katanya, saya sudi♪

123
00:04:47,518 --> 00:04:51,858
♪Mentari terbenam merapati awak
untuk mendengar bisikan awak♪

124
00:04:51,858 --> 00:04:57,018
♪Terlalu banyak rahsia
diluahkan kepada awak♪

125
00:04:57,688 --> 00:04:59,998
♪Manis sangat♪

126
00:04:59,998 --> 00:05:02,378
♪Gugusan bintang berkerdipan demi awak♪


